kdna-web-client
Copyright 2026 KDNA Authors

This product includes software developed at
https://github.com/aikdna/kdna-web-client

kdna-web-client provides browser-safe KDNA utilities: file selection,
metadata inspection, file upload, and load-plan state management.

This package never performs decryption or license verification.
All sensitive operations must be handled by a server running
@aikdna/kdna-web-server or an equivalent server-side integration.

See LICENSE for the full Apache 2.0 license text.
See README.md for the browser integration guide.
See docs/security-model.md for what this package does and does not do.
